react toastify 
npm i react-toastify >> this is to install react toastify 
after installation add 
 import 'react-toastify/dist/ReactToastify.css';
 at index.js
 and also add <ToastContainer/>
 tostify and notification has the same use so we can use any of them and also are o same process.
react tastify is one of the react packae while shows messae if we save delete or update and also if we make any changes to the website.
